","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36990,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/09\/25\/khawatim-determine-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":2526,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Khawatim: Final deeds determine fate in Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 25, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Sahl ibn Sa\u2019d reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the deeds are only judged by their endings.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6607 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari Imam Ibn al-Mulaqqin commented, \"Allah judges His servants in good and evil, such that He forgives\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21095,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/10\/25\/mawt-fear-hope-salvation\/","url_meta":{"origin":2526,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Death: Fear and hope at the time of death","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 25, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, entered the home of a young man in the throes of death. The Prophet said, \u201cHow do you feel?\u201d The man said, \u201cBy Allah, O Messenger of Allah, I hope in Allah and I fear for my sins.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u0